Question: An image shows five white pear shapes, and at least two are holding flowers.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: https://www.oliveandcocoa.com/images/uploads/4285-Porcelain-Pear-Vases-L.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many white pear shapes are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many white pear shapes are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there at least two pear shapes holding flowers?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there at least two pear shapes holding flowers?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 5 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 5 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
